-- Brazil to Auction Oil Exploration Areas in Weeks, Reuters Says
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r i s t o w
-- 2012-01-15T17:41:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-15/brazil-to-auction-oil-exploration-areas-in-weeks-reuters-says.html
Brazilian President  Dilma Rousseff 
will authorize an auction of 174 oil and natural-gas exploration
areas “within a few weeks,”  Reuters said , citing an interview
with Energy Minister Edison Lobao in Abu Dhabi.  Half of the concessions are onshore and half are offshore,
the news service quoted Lobao as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Bristow in Brasilia at 
 mbristow5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sylvia Wier at 
 swier@bloomberg.net  